@startuml
title UC15 - Backend Classes
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
class PasswordResetController {
  +requestReset(request): Response
  +reset(request): Response
}
class PasswordResetService {
  +requestReset(email): void
  +reset(token, newPassword): void
  -validatePolicy(password): void
}
class UserRepository {
  +findByEmail(email): User
  +updatePassword(userId, hash): void
}
class PasswordResetTokenRepository {
  +create(userId, tokenHash, expiresAt): PasswordResetToken
  +findValidByHash(tokenHash): PasswordResetToken
  +markUsed(id): void
}
class EmailService { +sendResetLink(email, rawToken): void }
class PasswordHasher { +hash(password): String }
PasswordResetController --> PasswordResetService
PasswordResetService --> UserRepository
PasswordResetService --> PasswordResetTokenRepository
PasswordResetService --> EmailService
PasswordResetService --> PasswordHasher
note bottom of PasswordResetService
  requestReset: phản hồi trung lập (không lộ email tồn tại).
  Lưu token_hash, expires_at; token dùng-một-lần (BR31).
  reset: kiểm tra hash + not used/expired + password policy (>=8, chữ+số).
end note
note bottom of EmailService
  Email provider (server-side credentials). Gửi raw token trong link.
end note
@enduml
